{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"瑞果宋老师(原星星船)","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEkudePaicQia8AsbIwANrbSibSbYqBMz6s2KOM0StEDiaRw8uian63mRsn2zHDWxx8dSicmeicq4XRsIrpg/0","content":"不对，我有权在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为。并不意味着，我就有权重婚，因为性行为是一个，只要双方同意不管是，同性还是异性，都是基于双方同意的情况下，她生了一个，个体自愿的行为，而重婚罪违反国家的法律，这是性质完全不一样的两种事情，属于滑坡谬误","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7901,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492439400000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"梅林君","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7FvPplUlLxoNThcwuibAPfKujKYNekpvUMWUh7H6tWxbHDiaQ8Ia188iabaz7NMiaKYVoY8ZSAyytMTQ/0","content":"同性性行为与多婚乱伦有什么因果关系吗？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7797,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492333278000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"迷迭香","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bWV5FUyboCIOk2icGvegOZ7qmwDXVPlm0pmyu0tuemmkIaDqE1O6xCdX1tVMLNtwTvuVYVOMKQG3A/0","content":"这位参议院的推论站不住脚。因为重婚、多婚、乱伦、通奸等属于公认的违背道德甚至违法行为，而同性性行为目前尚未明确定论，其是否具有社会危害性、危害性大小也尚且是个存在争议的问题。从有权自愿发生同性性行为就推导出以下一系列行为合理，是滑坡谬误。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7687,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492135193000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"DearJoey","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzXrk7kxiaxiarcZtoK5ibGvfiaxSOc4AUm4uYjslRRZQg8yWScKHibVDOuOqxTZic5HfXm3wFhibAvyqMy/0","content":"站不住脚。发生同性性行为并不意味着会结婚，那就不存在重婚和多婚的问题。再者，即使是异性性行为也有可能有乱伦和通奸的情况，不能把这作为同意同性性行为之后发生的必然结果。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7432,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491738090000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"<p>这个是典型的滑坡谬误，有A推出B，B推C...， 但是每个推论的逻辑关系都很脆弱。</p><p>假设有权多婚，是否就有权做任何事情呢，当然不是，逻辑关系不成立。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7336,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491536190000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"东润家具邝利云","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjOkia7eibkITySvUExH5dicgdSdEHl6Y1FLwVWDq7XOjt0EbfuA0EIVRVGCgKLzyU1mIhTtk3AYMl8R/0","content":"同意同性性行为，反对重婚，乱伦，通奸。同性性行为属为双方意志问题，不存在第三方，不对其他人造成影响。重婚本身就对第三方造成伤害，乱伦那就是道德界限，通奸就涉及法律，有权做任何事就涉及法律了，社会保障了。用意志扩大到社会，那就不是个人问题了。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7227,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491371354000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"盛夏tl","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQLZSOLpBibDcibZ6sFXGjaugXibNJwMAvZF35uJNo0TzNd8uGdLrfymhDiav0qNFFCZzEIQIxyrWNEPw/0","content":"人权也要遵循道德的约束","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7194,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491308118000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQEYBMtN5kb4OpmTENFEHLicFEIfy1kicpbhTZrnQtdSqeU7tIpxhB6XZZHZ4qymOJbAxuiaaokM2GAq/0","content":"这是一种滑坡谬误，从同性性行为推论到重婚和乱伦，而这些行为之间完全没有必然性联系，甚至可能性都很低，所以这个推论并不成立。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7178,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491291763000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"kerry","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-02","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5cUlGv2ibxydlESCOjsMG6yNquicDV2grtRHY4e6BREibMTu7aYqiaYHGMSVmVfneOdxIhRkLicP5at1/0","content":"我持反对意见，有两点原因，一是前者的行为属于个人自愿选择，且未对他人造成伤害和影响，也不算违法。而后者作者延展提到的行为，伤害到其他人并且违法。已经不是同一个范畴的事情做讨论，滑坡理论提到了不相关的话题了。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7096,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491114920000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"咕咕","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoAOwic4GNKoz5oR3ECE0v0lAicujK9wBbRPMVWrjBNRath8ZicUnKVKP1TicLlXAlKrf2HJNO0Vv5SH5/0","content":"发生同性性行为，不等于重婚、多婚、乱伦、通奸，有发生前者的权利，不等于一定会发生后者，更不能推出有权做任何事的结论。这种说法混淆了合法与非法，也把可能当作了必然，并得出了最坏的情况作结论，是典型的滑坡谬误。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5049,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490971760000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":" 法律规定，不可以重婚、不可以乱伦、不可以通奸。同性性行为也应当在符合法律的规定下进行。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6472,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490750573000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"锦慕兰","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS3skBBT8HsSPCyTJe0kT5cTVYOdIHeuEGdvfS3eHvDbZuYZcRIMxiaz0lVQjiadx2BdTtgw0bzCCn0/0","content":"我持反对意见，这位前参议员的推论是站不住脚的。假设的前提和结论没有一连串必然的联系，这是一个滑坡谬误。恶意解读了最高法院的说法，夸张了结果。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6032,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490601449000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"田若宁","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLqGerKFuywibK8LCiawbEekbVKdkH4LYgCbm2X0D0OEwZ5SPthaibL2mdxMthlyw2eNRiaIKIPUqj2q0I6fMOiczTt7/0","content":"Rick其实是在暗示重婚，多婚，乱伦，通奸是不合法是不应该发生的，因此“在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为”也是不应该的。将可能性当成必然性这是滑坡谬误。\n\n重婚，多婚，通奸已经是受到法律限制的行为（乱伦如果涉及到未成年人受到法律限制，如果是成年人则是道德层面），而同性性行为是两个人之间自然的行为，性质不同，不可能由最高法院判决“你有权在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为”合法，而自动产生“多婚”、“重婚”合法的结果。\n\n更不可能当最高法院判决“在自己的房间里发生双方同意的同性性行为”合法时，你就有权做任何事。如果你认为你有权做任何事，其中包括触及法律的事，那么你将失去自由。只有在遵守法律的前提下才享有权利和自由。\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5108,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490574557000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoKhVPxI6DpwnHKKPJt17dRFOPWYiaPRuibicWpE8buPW3ogdyicLDZaylR8tx6hlSgp9Q22tM03mmiaX6/0","content":"我认为前参议院的推论站不住脚，因为同性性行为和重婚之间没有必然联系，有权同性行为并不能说明有权重婚，同理，重婚，多婚，乱伦，通奸之间并没有必然联系，所以推论不能成立。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4591,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490236181000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6Kq7NwJg01KPhAdTxrtB27YOCDyNYflqVmOChkOmM1s8UJogTLQGWiaichDH2J1MHWWX9TCzzgwDAYgS/0","content":"反对。\n同性性行为 重婚 多婚 乱伦 通奸 等等都属于有争议的社会问题。\n最高法院说人们有权发生同性性行为，不代表其他有争议的社会问题也被允许。\n同性性行为连带着的一定是重婚 多婚的罪恶吗？他们没有必然联系，参议员夸大其词。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4641,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490109561000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"El.","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELtgmmibEickAfib5gqpJia8eU8BgdbpVtiagqzjkIicRzLOPibmwSE22mQu8xa8JUuRPfTmg89bY3JpCzFQ/0","content":"重婚多婚等属法律明确禁止，乱伦通奸等需要道德约束，而且并没有法律明确规定禁止乱伦通奸，也就是乱伦通奸受道德批判，重婚多婚会受法律制裁，更不要提可以做任何事了，简直没有任何联系。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4805,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490107688000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lea","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5P1aL6srAd0Yn27aicxwR5Klsx7PtSR6sT6xwdyJ6HTcfeSia8AoMiakMffEhOWzic6GO2lRIiaclOZa/0","content":"滑坡谬误，这个推论肯定是站不住脚的，他拿双方同意的同性性行为来推论出后面的结论太单薄，没有和后面问题有必然联系，不能说双方同意的同性性行为，就一定会重婚、多婚、乱伦、通奸这些行为，所以是没有道理的，不可信","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4394,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489974591000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"缪能达","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLBfJaFAXv169oBrne60t4iaWXzpMsZychdeFGVLsoERXbZF9MnP7Dgx7YibMwXPn8rjtUBg8iaZPEPrmBIJb7sQJpTDjBTy5I7hnQ/0","content":"这个推论并站不住脚，因违反了滑坡谬误。\n\n同意同性性行为，并不是主观上的支持，也跟自己是否有权去重婚没有因果关系，同理后面的多婚、乱伦和通奸的论述之间也没有强相关，都是这个前参议员自己YY出来的。这样的推理属于滑坡谬误。（其实有些地方在我看来甚至没有逻辑可言）","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2879,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489036265000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM6nOlVFgMKicVRUia54mssmloGh0KvYD5Y5lt4wibRMMsZtUPpl2qCFFP8Htv3xUYf2kcUupGe8gjVqg/0","content":"前参议员强调的是“在自己房间发生双方都同意的同性性行为”，我认为“双方都同意”是关键。但，紧接着，前参议员就得出有权“重婚、多婚、乱伦、通奸”等观点，我认为此论证完全不合理，并无理由或证据支撑。推论站不住脚，理由如下：\n\n1、重婚、多婚、乱伦、通奸等发生的前提也是双方愿意同意吗？如果只是单方的行为或意愿，你就没有权利做这些事。\n\n2、即使你的另一半同意你重婚，从法律、伦理道德层面来说，这点是不成立的。\n\n3、同性恋与异性恋都是人们对性取向不同的方式，不同的性取向都是值得尊重的；在一些国家或城市，同性恋结婚也是合法化。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2501,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1488509370000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Iris","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7dCoiaibWo9zOF3tmaiaB2uhDut0wnHDSUKNYzAI8UpcmgAA5Q5kFyaseGpWsqcVqTpEIz2GbtkuVvA/0","content":"滑坡谬误：即不合理地使用连串的因果关系，将“可能性”转化为“必然性”，从而得到不合理的结论。\n在别人抛出一连串推论时，要求对方描述清楚，这个结果到底如何产生，或者自己思考，有什么理由让这个推论不成立。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":2497,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1488508432000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
